About key largo conch house
Key Largo Conch House
A second generation, family owned and operated, seafood restaurant and wedding caterer since 2004.
Our caring and committed staff is excited to present their vision to you. They want you have a fantastic experience and enjoy fresh, local seafood.
We've been featured on The Travel Channel, Food Network, Emeril's Florida, how to DO florida, Florida Keys Best Restaurants and more.
Come find out why we're getting all this attention!
Key Largo & Islamorada Catering
Planning an event in the Florida Keys? Contact us today! We specialize in wedding catering and special events catering - servicing Key Largo and Islamorada in the Florida Keys. Be sure to follow us on Instagram for great catering ideas!
@klconchhouse_events
Florida Keys Catering Menus
Seasonal and Local
We refuse to compromise on quality in our seafood restaurant. That's why we source our fresh ingredients from local farmers and seafood markets. No matter what time of year, you can be sure you're eating the best of the season!
Fresh, local seafood and produce is our motto. We have the same standards for coffee. We only serve Segafredo, so come by for a latte, cappuccino or espresso. Voted best coffee in Key Largo every year!
Travel Channel, Food Network, Emeril's Florida and more...
